Preconditions:
- The input array `nums` is not null.
- The length of the input array `nums` is even.

Postconditions:
- The method returns an integer representing the maximized sum.
- The pairs `(a1, b1), (a2, b2), ..., (an, bn)` are formed from the input array `nums`.
- The sum of `min(ai, bi)` for all `i` is maximized.